F-Droid Repository

This is the official F-Droid repository for KeyMatch and ContentCreator apps. KeyMatch is a dating app focused on meaningful connections through intelligent matching and detailed profiles. ContentCreator is a powerful app for creating, editing, and managing digital content with AI-powered features.

Currently it serves 2 apps. To add it to your F-Droid app, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this link:

https://klas96.github.io/fdroid/repo
